title: For Sale:  Taser M26C
postcontent: The TASER® M26C is modeled after police model TASER® M26C M26. It combines the injury reducing benefits of traditional stun technology with a quantum leap in stopping power via new Electro-Muscular Disruption (EMD) technology. In police studies, the new TASER® M26C has a higher instant incapacitation rate than a 9mm hand gun. The TASER® M26C shoots out 2 darts attached to 15 feet of wire. 50,000 volts travels over the wires and over-rides the central nervous system providing incredible takedown power. Package includes includes:  One (1) TASER® M26C with Integrated Laser Sight  Four (4) Air Cartridges One (1) Carrying case  (Note: Requires 8 AA batteries which are NOT included.)NEW Electro-Muscular Disruption (EMD) TechnologyThere are two catagories of energy weapons: Stun weapons and EMD weapons.STUN WEAPONS: Traditional stun technology weapons operate in a 7-14 Watt range and interfere with the communication signals within the nervous system of the target. These stun systems primarily effect the sensory nervous system. Like static on the communication lines between the brain and the body, stun systems interfere with the human command and control systems. However, a small percentage of people with a very high tolerance for electrical stimulation can fight through the effect of these 7-14 Watt systems. The TASER® 44001 series is a stun weapon using the same settings used by law enforcement for over 20 years.EMD WEAPONS: EMD weapons use a more powerful 16 - 26 Watt electrical signal to completely override the central nervous system and directly control the skeletal muscles. This EMD effect causes an uncontrollable contraction of the muscle tissue, allowing the M-Series to physically debilitate a target regardless of pain tolerance or mental focus.The TASER® M-Series are EMD weapons -- specifically designed to stop even the most elite, aggressive, focused combatants. Rather than simply interfering with communication between the brain and muscles, the TASER® EMD systems directly tell the muscles what to do: contract until the target is in the fetal position on the ground. The TASER® provides for maximum safety for both the user and the subject by bringing dangerous situations quickly under control before force escalates to lethal levels.

title: For Sale:  browning x-bolt 243 varmint
postcontent: i have a browning xbolt .243 winchester for sale.   fired maybe 200 times.   very accurate with 100 grain and under bullets; shoots round nose 105's excellent as well.   i can not use the heavy 105 match bullets in this gun, so it doesnt get used.   it's an awesome rifle.....heavy enough to shoot very accurately, not too heavy to take on a normal deer hunt.   this gun is Basically a heavy barreled deer rifle.   not really as heavy as you would think it would be.   anyway....i have shot several 1 inch groups at 300 yards, most rifles are doing well to shoot that at 100 yards.   this one does it with a variety of bullet weights and powders.   it doesnt seem finicky at all...it just will not fire the bullets i want.    i am very confident that with a better scope, this rifle could do better than 1 inch at 300.   my eyes need more than 10x to shoot better than that...but with a better scope, this one could do it.   scope mounts included with this rifle.
